OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry although rather cloudy
OL,6,Fday, but some bright or sunny spells
OL,7,Fdeveloping by afternoon in the south
OL,8,Fand east. Becoming warm in the
OL,9,Fsunshine.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry with
OL,12,Fsome late brightness in places. Then
OL,13,Fthe rest of the night will be dry with
OL,14,Fvariable amounts of cloud.
OL,15,
OL,16,CThursday:FA dry day on Thursday with
OL,17,Fsome bright or sunny spells developing
OL,18,Fby afternoon. Warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
